          "action": "escalate_to_human",
          "handoffTarget": "reliability_engineer",
          "rationale": "Zone D means damage is probable with continued operation; on a constraint asset the run/shutdown tradeoff is a senior reliability call weighing catastrophic failure against lost throughput."
