          "action": "escalate_to_human",
          "handoffTarget": "authorized_inspector",
          "rationale": "ASME/NBIC jurisdictional equipment may not be repaired ad hoc — repairs need an authorized inspector and an R-stamp holder, and an improper weld repair is a life-safety event."
        }
